## About This Modified Version

This is a modified version of CrazyCrates, maintained by KillGoddess.

### Original Project
- Repository: https://github.com/Crazy-Crew/CrazyCrates
- Author: CrazyCrew
- License: MIT License

### Modified Version
- Repository: https://github.com/KillGoddess/zoo
- Maintainer: KillGoddess
- License: MIT License (inherited from original project)

### Modifications Include
- RandomBox crate animation (conveyor belt style)
- Five-pull feature (Shift + Right Click)
- Single-tier pity system (guarantee mechanism)
- Purpur 1.21.4 compatibility fixes
- Complete Chinese documentation

All modifications are released under the same MIT License as the original project.

